Package wordageddon.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Answer
    Represents a user's answer to a question in the Wordageddon game.
    DocumentTermMatrix
    Document-Term Matrix implementation for text analysis.
    GameDataContainer
    Container class that holds the Document Term Matrix along with the associated documents and stopwords.
    GameEngine
    Core game engine that manages the Wordageddon game logic and state.
    GameSession
    Represents a complete game session in Wordageddon.
    GameSessionSummary
    Data Transfer Object representing game session statistics for leaderboard display.
    Question
    Represents a question in the Wordageddon game with multiple choice options.
    TextAnalysisService
    Service for analyzing text documents and "tokenize" their content into a Document-Term Matrix (DTM).
    User
    Represents a user in the Wordageddon application.
    UserLeaderboardEntry
    Represents a user entry in the global leaderboard system.
